    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a really clear way to put it. I want to make sure my students understand the impact, though. Could you give me a few specific historical examples or supreme court cases where substantive due process was the key reason why certain rights were protected? Maybe something where it really changed the legal landscape for people's privacy or personal freedom.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
